Class SquareService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.rest.products.model.SquareService
  • @Component
public class SquareService
extends java.lang.Object
    Square service class. Uses CatalogWrapper's calls to interact with Square API and returns response to BackendService.
    See Also:
    BackendService, CatalogWrapper, SquareServiceException, SquareServiceResponseBody

        Parameters:
        request - A ProductPostRequestBody instance containing details of the request.
        Returns:
        A serialized response containing the information of this layer.
        Throws:
